snippet.title: Aurrery - 3D Techno Mixing
snippet.description:
Playing around mixing a techno track in 3D using Aurrery. Aurrery is now available on Steam early access!

Stems used are from  Joe Farr - Don't be afraid.
https://joefarr.bandcamp.com/track/dont-be-afraid
